[PNG2Clipboard]([Sanborn-Young/PNG2Clipboard: This utility allows you to take a Win11 Snipping Tool Screen Shot and paste it into any .md note as an embedded webp data stream.](https://github.com/Sanborn-Young/PNG2Clipboard)) allows you use the snipping tool in Win11, and it will replace the current clipboard contents with a b64 data stream that can be directly pasted into a markdown file as an embedded b64 data stream.
